dataTestModel$probabilities <- probabilities > .5
dataTestModel$prob <- dataTestModel$probabilities> 0
dataTestModel$prob[dataTestModel$probabilities == FALSE] <- 0
dataTestModel$prob[dataTestModel$prob == TRUE] <- 1

dataTestModel$w <- dataTestModel$whitey> 0
dataTestModel$w[dataTestModel$whitey == FALSE] <- 0
dataTestModel$w[dataTestModel$whitey == TRUE] <- 1
getClassifierPerformance <- function(model, real){ 
  
accuracy <- sum(real == model) / length(real)

falsePositive <- sum(model == TRUE & real == 0) / sum(real == 0)

falseNegative <- sum(model == FALSE & real == 1) / sum(real == 1)  

positivePredict <-  sum(model == TRUE & real == 1) / sum(model == TRUE)  

performance <- data.frame(Accuracy = accuracy, falsePositive = falsePositive, falseNegative = falseNegative, positivePredict = positivePredict)
return(performance)
}
getClassifierPerformance(dataTestModel$prob, dataTestModel$w)
